    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK113">
<l>naṉṟē tariṉu naṭuvikantā mākkattai</l>
<l>yaṉṟē yoḻiya viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if it gives great things, wealth that comes in breach of justice</l>
<l>one must give up immediately.</l>
